msg.msgText: NOTES: 1. "Name" is a required item. 2. All "Key=value" pair must be enclosed within double quotation marks. 3. For validation rules of "RuleType","Source", "Destination", and "RetainedMessages", refer to InfoCenter. 4. Disabling the rule stops the rule, which results in the loss of buffered messages and any messages that are currently being sent.
